title: Nas - I Am... Nastradamus (1999) [2-Disc Original]
description:
Couldn't find ANY good torrents that contained the full, original 2-disc album from Nas, so I decided to compile it myself. For any fans that haven't heard this version, do yourself a favour and experience what could have been one of hip-hops greatest double albums of all-time.

This version contains the original tracklistings and the songs that were ultimately cut from the retail versions of "I Am" and "Nastradamus"

Artist: Nas
Album: I Am... Nastradamus
Year: 1999
Discs: 2
Source: CDrip / iTunes / Web Download (only 2 tracks)
Bitrate: 256kbps - 320kbps (VBR)
